<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Jordan on OONI: Open Observatory of Network Interference</title><link>https://ooni.github.io/tags/jordan/</link><description>Recent content in Jordan on OONI: Open Observatory of Network Interference</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 20 Sep 2023 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ooni.github.io/tags/jordan/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Grindr blocked in Jordan: Shrinking LGBTQ spaces</title><link>https://ooni.github.io/post/2023-jordan-blocks-grindr/</link><pubDate>Wed, 20 Sep 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ooni.github.io/post/2023-jordan-blocks-grindr/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Jordan recently &lt;a href="https://explorer.ooni.org/m/20230808211935.881250_JO_webconnectivity_6b7549126aabe25d"&gt;blocked&lt;/a&gt; access to &lt;a href="https://www.grindr.com/"&gt;Grindr&lt;/a&gt; — the world’s largest social networking app for gay, bi, trans, and queer people — adding to the list of social media apps banned in the country, including &lt;a href="https://explorer.ooni.org/chart/mat?probe_cc=JO&amp;amp;since=2023-08-13&amp;amp;until=2023-09-13&amp;amp;time_grain=day&amp;amp;axis_x=measurement_start_day&amp;amp;test_name=web_connectivity&amp;amp;domain=www.tiktok.com"&gt;TikTok&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://explorer.ooni.org/chart/mat?probe_cc=JO&amp;amp;since=2023-08-13&amp;amp;until=2023-09-13&amp;amp;time_grain=day&amp;amp;axis_x=measurement_start_day&amp;amp;test_name=web_connectivity&amp;amp;domain=www.clubhouse.com"&gt;Clubhouse&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://explorer.ooni.org/chart/mat?probe_cc=JO&amp;amp;since=2023-08-01&amp;amp;until=2023-09-10&amp;amp;time_grain=day&amp;amp;axis_x=measurement_start_day&amp;amp;test_name=web_connectivity&amp;amp;domain=www.grindr.com"&gt;OONI network measurement data&lt;/a&gt; collected from Jordan suggests that ISPs started blocking access to Grindr on August 8th 2023, and that the block &lt;a href="https://explorer.ooni.org/chart/mat?probe_cc=JO&amp;amp;since=2023-08-01&amp;amp;until=2023-09-21&amp;amp;time_grain=day&amp;amp;axis_x=measurement_start_day&amp;amp;test_name=web_connectivity&amp;amp;domain=www.grindr.com"&gt;remains ongoing&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This report shares &lt;a href="https://explorer.ooni.org/chart/mat?probe_cc=JO&amp;amp;since=2023-08-01&amp;amp;until=2023-09-10&amp;amp;time_grain=day&amp;amp;axis_x=measurement_start_day&amp;amp;test_name=web_connectivity&amp;amp;domain=www.grindr.com"&gt;OONI data&lt;/a&gt; on the blocking of Grindr in Jordan.&lt;/p&gt;
